### Matter Power Spectrum P(k) at z=0

Comparison with CAMB HaloFit nonlinear P(k):

| k (h/Mpc) | P_sim (Mpc/h)³ | P_CAMB_NL | Ratio |
|---|---|---|---|
| 0.019 | 25,697 | 24,893 | 1.032 |
